title: Prince Deluxe Editions
description:
A collection of Prince albums uploaded to an old blog. These are all expanded versions of Prince's albums through 1992 with b-sides, remixes and unreleased things. Here is what you'll find inside:

1999
Around The World In A Day
Batman
The Black Album (24 Bit Vinyl Rip)
Camille
Controversy
Diamonds and Pearls
Dirty Mind
The Family - The Family (24 Bit Vinyl Rip)
For You
Good Love (24 Bit Vinyl Rip)
Graffiti Bridge
The Love Symbol Album
Lovesexy
NYC Live 1-11-97
Parade
Peach & Black: The Camille Anthology
Prince
Purple Rain
The Rebels - The Rebels
Sign "O" The Times
Sign "O" The Times (24 Bit Vinyl Rip)
The Time - Corporate World
Vanity 6 - Vanity 6
